Package com.app.converter.many.impl

Class ClientsConverterImpl

java.lang.Object
com.app.converter.many.impl.ClientsConverterImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientsConverter
@Component public class ClientsConverterImpl extends Object implements ClientsConverter
Implementation of the ClientsConverter interface for converting between different representations of clients.

This component handles the conversion of client data from entities to DTOs and vice versa. It also provides helper methods for grouping clients by category and associating clients with their respective debit amounts.
